channel.description:
Hey everyone firstly i would like to mention the base which is delta, pretty much ive re-written whole combat and tried to improve it as much as i could since it was bad. I've been working to this project long time ago but had this as a backup to do on sparetime since ive been working on another server.
What im looking for: Server side coders x2 pref(Lot of work to be done here) Website Designerx2 Gfx Artisx2

This is something of my work just as a proof http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rczEWxL3llM
